### Get all courses
GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/courses/

###

### Get course by ID
GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/courses/1

###

### Create a new course
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/courses/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Python Programming",
    "code": "CS102",
    "credits": 3
}

###

### Update a course
PUT http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/courses/2
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Advanced Python",
    "code": "CS102",
    "credits": 4
}

###

### Delete a course
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/courses/2